%% Agent Workflow - Complete Campaign Sequence
%% Shows sequential execution with context passing

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CreativeDirector
    participant BrandStrategist
    participant Copywriter
    participant Designer
    participant Critic
    participant ProjectManager

    User->>CreativeDirector: 📋 Campaign Brief<br/>(Product, Audience, Goal)

    Note over CreativeDirector: 🤔 PLANNING PHASE<br/>Analyze complexity<br/>Create 5-step plan

    CreativeDirector->>User: 📢 Present Plan:<br/>1. Market Research<br/>2. Copywriting<br/>3. Visual Design<br/>4. Quality Review<br/>5. Project Timeline

    Note over CreativeDirector: 🚀 EXECUTION PHASE<br/>Sequential with verification

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    CreativeDirector->>BrandStrategist: 🔍 Research market & competitors<br/>(Brief + context)
    BrandStrategist->>BrandStrategist: Use Google Search
    BrandStrategist->>CreativeDirector: ✅ Audience insights<br/>Competitor analysis<br/>Trending topics
    CreativeDirector->>User: ✓ Research complete
    end

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    CreativeDirector->>Copywriter: ✍️ Create 5 posts<br/>(Brief + insights from Step 1)
    Copywriter->>CreativeDirector: ✅ 5 Instagram posts<br/>Captions + Hashtags + CTAs
    CreativeDirector->>User: ✓ Copywriting complete
    end

    Note over CreativeDirector: 💾 Context Compaction Check<br/>After 3 agents: Summarize older context

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    CreativeDirector->>Designer: 🎨 Generate image prompts<br/>(Posts from Step 2)
    Designer->>CreativeDirector: ✅ Visual concepts<br/>Image generation prompts
    CreativeDirector->>User: ✓ Design complete
    end

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    CreativeDirector->>Critic: ⭐ Review all work<br/>(Strategy + Copy + Visuals)
    Critic->>CreativeDirector: ✅ Quality assessment<br/>Feedback + Ratings
    CreativeDirector->>User: ✓ Review complete
    end

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    CreativeDirector->>ProjectManager: 📋 Create timeline<br/>(Complete campaign details)
    ProjectManager->>ProjectManager: Create Notion pages
    ProjectManager->>CreativeDirector: ✅ Project plan<br/>Timeline + Tasks + Notion links
    CreativeDirector->>User: ✓ Timeline complete
    end

    Note over CreativeDirector: 📦 FINAL COMPILATION

    CreativeDirector->>User: 🎉 Complete Campaign:<br/>• Market Research<br/>• 5 Social Media Posts<br/>• Visual Concepts<br/>• Quality Review<br/>• Project Timeline
